{"tid":1329449,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★聽說可「搵大錢」買手機，支人黑工雙腳壓碎，父母家貧 望有心人士相助。","createTime":"2019-07-18T08:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T08:15:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bc20ffcf6808751bf2f69e2ca505d0b7309d4079","tid":1329449,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:12:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽說可「搵大錢」 付2萬中介費來港</span><br />\n<br />\n羅家一家四口為河南新縣人，羅父是農民，一邊眼晴失明，羅君豪就讀高中未畢業，另有一名年約30多歲的姊姊。羅媽媽指，兒子因聽別人說有人可介紹來港「搵大錢」，向一名中介人繳付2萬元介紹費後，上月3日由深圳來港，5日起於流浮山一個回收場內工作，日薪約600元，於上月20日及本月5日曾出糧共9,000多元，羅用了部分錢作租房<span style=\"color: red;\">及買手機</span>。惟於意外後，仍有約7,000多元欠薪未有支付。羅媽媽稱，當時兒子出發前未有通知家人，但到港後有致電回家，羅媽媽當時擔心兒子勸他回鄉，但兒子未有理會，不幸隨後發生意外。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望有熱心人士相助</span><br />\n<br />\n羅媽媽指兒子稱回收場內所有員工都是黑工，於發生意外後所有員工均即時逃去，沒有人替他報警，唯有一名姓劉的僱主為羅報警，但其後亦已失去蹤影。兒子入院後，昏迷兩日方甦醒，並通知身在內地的父母。<span style=\"color: red;\">羅父母於本周一來到香港，惟他們家境貧困</span>、人生路不熟，兩晚來只於公園躺睡，亦無錢買東西吃，「東西太貴，買不起吃不起，老公餓了一天，有個姐姐給我一個麵包我吃」，自己的雙程證於本周日（21日）到期後便要返回大陸，由於兒子並非本地人，留醫費用高昂，面對兒子高昂的醫藥費，羅父母均感到徬徨，希望有熱心人士能相助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/353267/%E9%BB%91%E5%B7%A5%E6%88%AA%E8%82%A2-20%E6%AD%B2%E9%BB%91%E5%B7%A5%E9%9B%99%E8%85%B3%E5%A3%93%E7%A2%8E%E4%B8%80%E6%88%AA%E8%82%A2-%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E5%93%AD%E5%B4%A9-%E4%BB%96%E6%80%8E%E8%B5%B0%E4%B8%8B%E5%8E%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F353267%2F%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%2588%25AA%25E8%2582%25A2-20%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E9%259B%2599%25E8%2585%25B3%25E5%25A3%2593%25E7%25A2%258E%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2588%25AA%25E8%2582%25A2-%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%2593%25AD%25E5%25B4%25A9-%25E4%25BB%2596%25E6%2580%258E%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258E%25BB&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyohk9ljSbOzVJb7ECUhiv3w%3D&h=fd71b0c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/353267/%E9%BB%91%E5%B7%A5%E6%88%AA%E8%82%A2-20%E6%AD%B2%E9%BB%91%E5%B7%A5%E9%9B%99%E8%85%B3%E5%A3%93%E7%A2%8E%E4%B8%80%E6%88%AA%E8%82%A2-%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E5%93%AD%E5%B4%A9-%E4%BB%96%E6%80%8E%E8%B5%B0%E4%B8%8B%E5%8E%BB</a>"},{"pid":"a8eee19ca20b6c7ec536c0b5e90c589f6213ac58","tid":1329449,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b874cb715a398f0a03aa90bc78e5f017ebfde3f7","tid":1329449,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0799f965f6bafbfd556b43db00ac9617845b2983","tid":1329449,"uid":91771,"like":1,"di